body:
Here's the files I'm using https://drive.google.com/open?id=1UMpIDh85myaJed0dWvkzlMd9cb3ZHSmx.

1. I download the data from https://drive.google.com/open?id=1OFx1QpVFx7A0JZA4GTgB4Rm1lIFDemlm
2. I download the model from https://github.com/tensorflow/models/blob/master/research/object_detection/g3doc/detection_model_zoo.md  .Put it in my folder.
3.I start the training with train.py. I put it in google drive.
